---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="2024-2025 Into the Deep">
    <main class="main-content">
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <h1 class="hero-title">2024-2025 Into the Deep</h1>
                <p class="hero-subtitle">Current Season Achievements</p>
                <p class="hero-description">
                    Our journey through the 2024-2025 FTC season "Into the Deep" has been filled with
                    innovation, teamwork, and outstanding achievements. From regional competitions to
                    championship appearances, see how TurboV8 has made waves this season.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Season Highlights</h2>
                        <div class="achievements-grid">
                            <div class="achievement-card featured">
                                <h3>FIRST Championship</h3>
                                <div class="achievement-details">
                                    <p class="achievement-rank">3rd Place Alliance</p>
                                    <p class="achievement-division">Ochoa Division</p>
                                    <p class="achievement-award">Control Award</p>
                                </div>
                                <p class="achievement-description">
                                    Competed at the highest level of FTC competition, showcasing our robot's
                                    capabilities and earning recognition for our control systems.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="achievement-card">
                                <h3>NorCal FTC Regional Championship</h3>
                                <div class="achievement-details">
                                    <p class="achievement-rank">Winning Alliance First Pick</p>
                                </div>
                                <p class="achievement-description">
                                    Selected as the first pick by the winning alliance captain,
                                    demonstrating our robot's competitive performance.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="achievement-card">
                                <h3>NorCal FTC East Bay League</h3>
                                <div class="achievement-details">
                                    <p class="achievement-rank">Winning Alliance Captain</p>
                                    <p class="achievement-award">Inspire 2nd Place</p>
                                </div>
                                <p class="achievement-description">
                                    Led our alliance to victory while earning recognition for our
                                    overall team excellence and community impact.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row mt-6">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h2 class="section-title">Robot Design</h2>
                        <div class="robot-info">
                            <div class="robot-image-placeholder">
                                <span>Robot Photo</span>
                            </div>
                            <h3>Design Philosophy</h3>
                            <p>
                                Our 2024-2025 robot was designed with versatility and reliability in mind.
                                We focused on creating a robust system capable of handling the unique
                                challenges of the "Into the Deep" game.
                            </p>
                            <h4>Key Features</h4>
                            <ul class="feature-list">
                                <li>Advanced intake system for game elements</li>
                                <li>Precise scoring mechanisms</li>
                                <li>Reliable autonomous routines</li>
                                <li>Durable drivetrain for consistent performance</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <br/>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h2 class="section-title">Game Strategy</h2>
                        <div class="strategy-info">
                            <h3>Into the Deep Challenge</h3>
                            <p>
                                The 2024-2025 game "Into the Deep" challenged teams to navigate underwater-themed
                                obstacles while scoring game elements in various zones. Our strategy focused on
                                maximizing points through efficient autonomous routines and strategic alliance play.
                            </p>
                            <h4>Our Approach</h4>
                            <ul class="strategy-list">
                                <li><strong>Autonomous:</strong> Consistent high-scoring routines</li>
                                <li><strong>TeleOp:</strong> Fast and accurate game element manipulation</li>
                                <li><strong>Endgame:</strong> Reliable climbing and positioning</li>
                                <li><strong>Alliance:</strong> Strong communication and coordination</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row mt-6">
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Competition Timeline</h2>
                        <div class="timeline">
                            <div class="timeline-item">
                                <div class="timeline-date">September 2024</div>
                                <div class="timeline-content">
                                    <h3>Season Kickoff</h3>
                                    <p>Game reveal and initial robot design brainstorming</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-item">
                                <div class="timeline-date">October 2024</div>
                                <div class="timeline-content">
                                    <h3>Build Season</h3>
                                    <p>Intensive robot construction and programming phase</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-item">
                                <div class="timeline-date">December 2024</div>
                                <div class="timeline-content">
                                    <h3>East Bay League</h3>
                                    <p>Winning Alliance Captain, Inspire 2nd Place</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-item">
                                <div class="timeline-date">February 2025</div>
                                <div class="timeline-content">
                                    <h3>Regional Championship</h3>
                                    <p>Winning Alliance First Pick</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="timeline-item">
                                <div class="timeline-date">April 2025</div>
                                <div class="timeline-content">
                                    <h3>FIRST Championship</h3>
                                    <p>3rd Place Alliance, Control Award</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row mt-6">
                    <div class="col-12">
                        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Team Growth</h2>
                        <div class="growth-stats">
                            <div class="stat-card">
                                <h3>Technical Skills</h3>
                                <p>Advanced CAD modeling, precision manufacturing, and complex programming</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stat-card">
                                <h3>Leadership</h3>
                                <p>Team members took on mentorship roles and led outreach initiatives</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stat-card">
                                <h3>Community Impact</h3>
                                <p>Expanded our Steam Workshop program and mentored 5 new FTC teams</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    .achievements-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .achievement-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .achievement-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .achievement-card.featured {
        border-color: var(--light-red);
        background: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .achievement-card h3 {
        color: var(--light-red);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .achievement-details {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .achievement-rank {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: white;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .achievement-division,
    .achievement-award {
        color: var(--light-red);
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .robot-info,
    .strategy-info {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    .robot-image-placeholder {
        width: 100%;
        height: 200px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 8px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .robot-info h3,
    .strategy-info h3 {
        color: var(--light-red);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    .robot-info h4,
    .strategy-info h4 {
        color: var(--light-red);
        margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .feature-list,
    .strategy-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .feature-list li,
    .strategy-list li {
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
    }

    .feature-list li::before,
    .strategy-list li::before {
        content: "â†’";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: var(--light-red);
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .timeline {
        position: relative;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 2rem auto;
    }

    .timeline::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        left: 50%;
        top: 0;
        bottom: 0;
        width: 2px;
        background: var(--light-red);
        transform: translateX(-50%);
    }

    .timeline-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 3rem;
        position: relative;
    }

    .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) {
        flex-direction: row;
    }

    .timeline-item:nth-child(even) {
        flex-direction: row-reverse;
    }

    .timeline-date {
        flex: 0 0 150px;
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--light-red);
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .timeline-content {
        flex: 1;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        margin: 0 2rem;
        position: relative;
    }

    .timeline-content h3 {
        color: var(--light-red);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .timeline-content::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        width: 12px;
        height: 12px;
        background: var(--light-red);
        border-radius: 50%;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
    }

    .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) .timeline-content::before {
        right: -2rem;
    }

    .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content::before {
        left: -2rem;
    }

    .growth-stats {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .stat-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 2rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        text-align: center;
    }

    .stat-card h3 {
        color: var(--light-red);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .timeline::before {
            left: 20px;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            flex-direction: column !important;
            align-items: flex-start;
            padding-left: 40px;
        }

        .timeline-date {
            flex: none;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .timeline-content {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .timeline-content::before {
            left: -2rem !important;
        }
    }
</style>